12fe397f3fcf704f2596f698105323c9","slug":"compilation","date":"2021-10-17T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T14:03:35.418Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/compilation.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/compilation/cover.png","text":"这次讲一个可以说过时，但是也可以说永不过时的内容：C&#x2F;C++的编译与链接。说它过时，因为我们学习C语言的时候，第一个讲的就是这个知识点；而它不过时，是因为它是程序运行的基础。比如在一个C&#x2F;C++工程中，可能会有很多的 .c/.cpp、.h/.hpp文件，这时候...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.6k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"专业拓展","slug":"专业拓展","count":27,"path":"api/categories/专业拓展.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C语言复习","slug":"C语言复习","count":3,"path":"api/tags/C语言复习.json"},{"name":"C++程序设计","slug":"C-程序设计","count":9,"path":"api/tags/C-程序设计.json"},{"name":"make","slug":"make","count":1,"path":"api/tags/make.json"}],"author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}}}}